# CFURLEnumeratorGetSourceDidChange(_:)

**Function**

This function is unimplemented, so it performs no operation.

## Declaration

```swift
func CFURLEnumeratorGetSourceDidChange(_ enumerator: CFURLEnumerator!) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **enumerator**: The enumerator.

## Return Value

Returns `false`.

## Discussion

Use the File System Events API to detect changes to the file system. See [https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/Darwin/Conceptual/FSEvents_ProgGuide/Introduction/Introduction.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40005289] for more information.
